Manual Install

- create a new plugin
- paste the code -> plugin.php
- check the OnWebPagePrerender System Event
- create a Property Set: onTemplates [Texfield] [Comma separated list of template IDs] - property to specify the templates you want to run this plugin on

Package Install

- upload the file manually to core/packages/
- in the Package Management click "Add New Package"
- select the "Search Locally for Packages" option
- Anchors Away will appear in the Package list
- install